<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>There'll be singing</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hvilken jubel, hvilken glede
 når Guds hellige går inn,
 i Jerusalem, i Jerusalem.
 Seierspalmen lett vi svinger,
 skuer Jesus som Han er.
 I vår Guds Jerusalem.

[V2]
 There'll be singing,
 there'll be shouting
 when the saints go marching in,
 in Jerusalem, in Jerusalem.
 Waving palms with
 loud Hosiannas,
 as the King shall take His throne.
 In the new Jerusalem.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<title>Hvilken jubel, hvilken glede</title>
<presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
</song>